description.displayText: Dayanna worked for me a few years back when I had twins. Me and wife adored her. Honestly speaking I would highly recommend her to any family. Great with activities. Extremely reliable. Very respectful. She still comes to birthday parties for my children till this day. Dayanna wish you the best.

description.displayText: Dayanna is a very trust worthy, reliable, dedicated, caring and compassionate, easy to get along with person.  She is very devoted to work and home and finds the time to be there for family and friends, unconditionally.
